ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: For a student planning to research any of the 4th floor Becton labs, this class is a must.
Yes, if you'd like a tremendous amount of information on microwave circuits to be conveyed to you.
I would recommend AP816 to others who need microwave measurements since it's quite helpful.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Course gave a great overview of microwave electronics.
It exposed me to the tricks of the trade of microwave engineering.
This conveyed a tremendous amount of information on microwave circuits. My research is improved by a tremendous amount of information on microwave circuits being conveyed to me.
This course helps me get deeper understanding about the microwave measurement, which is frequently used in my experiments.
